==事件過程==
在1989年12月，居住在靠近[[伊朗|伊朗]]的阿塞拜疆人拆除了邊界的圍攔，訴求與伊朗境內的阿塞拜疆人建立更緊密的聯繫。{{link-en|贾利拉巴德|Cəlilabad|贾利拉巴德}}當地政府向暴動人群屈服，將權利移交給{{link-en|阿塞拜疆人民陣線|Azerbaijani Popular Front Party}}。由此，兩週後，在非暴力的情況下[[連科蘭|連科蘭]]的權利也被阿塞拜疆人民陣線接管了<ref name="NYT">{{cite news |url= https://www.nytimes.com/1990/01/29/world/upheaval-east-soviet-union-force-last-resort-armed-power-salvages-moscow-s.html?pagewanted=2 |title= UPHEAVAL IN THE EAST: SOVIET UNION; Force as a Last Resort: Armed Power Salvages Moscow's Facing Authority |newspaper= [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |author= Bill Keller |date= 28 January 1990 |access-date= 20 January 2010 |archive-date= 2021-03-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210308135509/https://www.nytimes.com/1990/01/29/world/upheaval-east-soviet-union-force-last-resort-armed-power-salvages-moscow-s.html?pagewanted=2 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

在1990年1月9號，[[亞美尼亞|亞美尼亞]][[最高苏维埃|最高苏维埃]]投票決定將[[納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫|納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫]]地區納入其預算負責範圍，並且允許納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫地區的居民在亞美尼亞選舉中投票。這個行為沒有經過蘇聯的許可，也侵害了[[阿塞拜疆苏维埃社会主义共和国|阿塞拜疆苏维埃社会主义共和国]][[最高苏维埃|最高苏维埃]]的統治。<ref name=Croissant>{{Cite book | first = Croissant | last = Michael P. | title = The Armenia-Azerbaijan Conflict: causes and implications | place = United States of America | publisher = Praeger Publishers | year = 1998 | pages = 36, 37 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=ZeP7OZZswtcC&q=17000&pg=PP1 | isbn = 0-275-96241-5 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | archive-date = 2021-11-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211128100559/https://books.google.com/books?id=ZeP7OZZswtcC&q=17000&pg=PP1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>這個舉動演變成全國性的騷動。隨後這引發了亞美尼亞境內要求阿塞拜疆共產黨官員移交權利，並且訴求獨立的遊行。在同一時刻，特別是阿塞拜疆的首都[[巴庫|巴庫]]，阿塞拜疆人民陣線舉行了大規模的反亞美尼亞人遊行，根據[[人權觀察|人權觀察]]的報告，當中言論是：「非常反亞美尼亞人的」。<ref name=hrw>{{Cite web |url=http://hrw.org/reports/1995/communal/ |title=Human Rights Watch. "Playing the "Communal Card": Communal Violence and Human Rights" |access-date=2022-01-21 |archive-date=2012-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011042435/http://www.hrw.org/reports/1995/communal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在一月12日，阿塞拜疆人民陣線在[[巴庫|巴庫]]組織了包括工廠和官員分部的國防委員會，希望動員阿塞拜疆人來攻擊當地亞美尼亞人。<ref name="NYT"/>

阿塞拜疆當局因為國內的分歧和不滿，無力恢復秩序。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JoGrR_9o3SUC&pg=PA96&dq=gorbachev+baku+1990+yazov+soldiers&lr=&cd=16#v=onepage&q=&f=false |title=On My Country and the World, Mikhail Gorbachev |access-date=2022-01-21 |archive-date=2022-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121061903/https://books.google.com/books?id=JoGrR_9o3SUC&pg=PA96&dq=gorbachev+baku+1990+yazov+soldiers&lr=&cd=16#v=onepage&q=&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>阿塞拜疆當局命令一萬兩千多人的內務部隊不要捲入在[[巴庫|巴庫]]的騷亂<ref>{{Cite book | first = Singh | last = Anita Inder | title = Democracy, ethnic diversity, and security in post-communist Europe | place = Berlin | publisher = Praeger Publishers | year = 2001 | page = 61 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=nU3bO8uiBn0C&q=Interior+Ministry | isbn = 0-275-97258-5 | access-date = 2022-01-21 | archive-date = 2022-01-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220121061900/https://books.google.com/books?id=nU3bO8uiBn0C&q=Interior+Ministry | dead-url = no }}</ref>，數個駐紮在[[巴庫|巴庫]]的蘇聯軍隊和[[里海区舰队|里海区舰队]]的海軍部隊，也沒有去阻止騷亂，表示沒有來自莫斯科的命令。<ref name="NYT"/>

